- Use Jotai when state is shared across files/routes.
- Local component state stays local.
- Co-locate atoms/selectors near their domain (e.g., src/state/<domain>.ts).
- Keep atoms minimal; derive with selectors where possible.

Refer to documentation and best practices here:
Docs: https://jotai.org/docs